scene.message:
Maki: We gotta hurry!{nl}
{wait_fr:60}...Hey, what's a{nl}
"police" again?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...It's a public{nl}
institution that maintains{nl}
social order. In this{nl}
case, the building.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Ah...{nl}
I think I remember{nl}
now... maybe?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Whoa!{nl}
What's that gym out back?!{nl}
When did that get built?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...While you were{nl}
in hospital. It's been{nl}
done about half a year.{nl}
Can't blame you.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I keep saying{nl}
I'm not hospitalized!{nl}
You're the joker here!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:80}Hey {ctl0f:1},{nl}
is she amnesiac?{nl}
She'd just slow us down.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: What are you two{nl}
mumbling about?! Hurry up,{nl}
Inaba's in danger!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon: Bwa ha ha!{nl}
You're the ones in danger!{nl}
I'll eat you up!{waitkey}{ret}
